                    <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                    <p>On May 8, the <hi rend="italic">Ad Hoc</hi> Committee on Armaments and
                        American Policy of the National Security Council submitted its preliminary
                        Report on Armaments and American Policy, designated <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 151. For <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 151 and
                        related documentation, see <ref target="frus1952-54v02p2#pg_845">pages
                            845</ref> ff.</p>
